Package com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3

package com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3

This meta-package contains all the packages used to run the Archive Server application. Logic is organized into the following packages:

  • configs -> Contains annotation-based configuration files for Spring Boot.
  • controllers -> Contains controllers for Spring Boot application.
  • core -> Contains core logic for AO3 story retrieval.
  • exceptions -> Contains custom exceptions for Archive Server application.
  • models -> Contains data models for Archive Server backend.
  • repositories -> Contains logic for persistent data storage.
  • services -> Contains services that drive Archive Server functionality.

The server application is entered into from the ArchiveServer top-level class.

Since:
